Here are two quick response drafts to keep engagement going:  

### **Response to Noah Gold:**

### **Response to David Torres, PhD:**  
_"Thanks, David! I’m familiar with Winning by Design but haven’t dug into Jacco’s AI-powered GTM work yet—definitely adding that to my research. If you’ve seen any standout insights or specific applications, would love to hear!"_  

Both keep the conversation open-ended and invite further discussion. Let me know if you want to tweak anything! 🚀
